{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, these combinations create a powerful predictive model that can takes advantage of the strengths of each approach.",
    "Student's academic performance prediction models have been tested and evaluated using a number of public and private online platforms, such as MOOCs, LMSs, and other learning platforms.",
    "These platforms contain data on how students learn and interact as well as their achievements.",
    "Cs offered by universities or any other educational institutions cover a wide range of subjects from fundamental skills to advanced courses based on student's own needs and preferences, regardless of their experience which allows them to learn new skills or brush up on their knowledge.",
    "However, it may be challenging to receive individualized attention from instructors in MOOCs because of the large number of students."
  ]
}